QuestData.Title: Mark of the Demon
QuestData.Description: The demonic rune glows in your hand, emanating dark power. A single word, inscribed in demon tongue, glows coldly... $b$b...GRAVAX...
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Demonic Emblem to Isoraen Nightstar at the Temple of Elune.
QuestData.RewardText: I am impressed that you were able to defeat such a powerful demon. We are fortunate that you have lent us your aid.
